nodes.text: The Pantoran Jedi Knight Toro Irana, high on the spice tempest, got into a brawl with the patrons of a restaurant on the planet Makem Te in 19 ABY. The Jedi killed a Swokes Swokes known as Choka Chok in the fighting as well as several others. Irana himself died when he misjudged his momentum and went flying through the restaurant's plate glass window, plummeting 40 stories to his death.
